==English==

Laughter is funny


===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang}} {{term|hlæhhan}}, {{term|hlihhan}}, {{term|hliehhan}}, cognate with Old Norse {{term|hlæja}} (Danish, Norwegian, Swedish {{term|le|lang=no}}), Old High German {{term|hlahhan}} (German {{term|lachen}}), Gothic {{term|𐌷𐌻𐌰𐌷𐌾𐌰𐌽|sc=Goth|tr=hlahjan}}.

